Hi, I was looking up our deep rl course to see if any updates were posted for undergrad enrollment.

Noticed that the website was updated, here http://rail.eecs.berkeley.edu/deeprlcourse/ with a sign-up form at the top. 

Good luck, and sorry if this was posted already.
